      "designMd": "WalkMate v2 — Korean walking healthcare app for office workers (Workon recruiting target).\n\nBrand: emerald primary (#16A34A) for walking domain, amber (#FBBF24) for ranking achievement, blue (#60A5FA) for location/GPS, rose (#EF4444) for stop/error.\n\nKey decisions captured in mapping-rationale.md:\n- DynamicColors disabled (preserve emerald brand identity)\n- Pretendard Variable font for Korean readability (line-height 1.5)\n- 3-tier corner radii: 12dp Button, 16dp Card, 24dp Hero/BottomSheet\n- onTertiary uses dark text #0B2540 (not white) for WCAG AA contrast\n- onPrimary white kept at 3.30:1 — accepted trade-off for brand vibrancy (M3 baseline emerald-700 darker would lose brand)\n\nAudit: 23 custom domain tokens (route/location/HC/ranking/step/chart) + 34 M3 tokens, light + dark parity verified.",
